==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-sketchy.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
'''sketchy'''

# Roughly or hastily laid out; intended for later refinement.
#:''The first draft included a '''sketchy''' design.''
# Of questionable or doubtful quality.
#:''The '''sketchy''' repair job did not look like it would hold.''
# (''of a person'') Suspected of taking part in ilicit or dishonorable dealings.
#:''Will is not '''sketchy''', as he does not take part in ilicit or dishonorable dealings.''

